snippet.title: Amber Heard Looks Sloppy!
snippet.description:
January Jones, Emily Blunt, and Amber Heard all get an F on this week's Fashion Offenders hosted by Wonderwall's Kirby Kristen.


SUBSCRIBE! http://goo.gl/iyC0ci

From washed out Winter wardrobes to sloppy style statements; we’ve rounded up this week’s worst dressed A-listers. January Jones, Emily Blunt, and Amber Heard are this week's Fashion Offenders. 

What do you think of January Jones' washed out look?  

Are you a fan of Emily Blunt's half cape Alexander McQueen Gown? Do you think Amber Heard looks sloppy or chic? 
 
About the series: Despite their entourages of specialists, celebs make fashion blunders just like the rest of us. Take a look as Wonderwall showcases the worst fashion fails of the week in just 60 seconds! Don't forget to tune in each week to find out if your favorite celebrity will score an F on "Fashion Offenders," hosted by Kirby Kristen.
